Name: Kenosha Public Market
Description:
Kenosha Public Market is a year-round Saturday market located in the heart of the Downtown district. Our vendors present a variety of products including local produce, artisan pastries and confections, locally sourced meats, poultry and eggs, fine cheeses, prepared foods & handmade gifts. Order from our online store, KPM2GO, to ensure you get the products you want before they sell out. Place orders during the week and pick up at our Saturday market! 
Our location is in the center of this pedestrian-friendly neighborhood with convenient parking options, world-class museums, an authentic streetcar system, two lighthouses, unique dining, and plenty of shopping options. Kenosha Public Market is proud to be one of the many shopping destinations Downtown.
Address: 625 52nd Street, Kenosha, WI, USA

Name: Downtown Beloit Farmers' Market - Summer
Description:
Our outdoor market starts the first Saturday in May and ends the last Saturday in October. Our indoor market starts the first Saturday in November and ends the last Saturday in April. Our current hours of operation are 9 am to noon, rain or shine. See less
An award-winning community tradition!
Live music at Gantry Park!
Shop in a wonderful open-air market in the heart of historic Downtown Beloit. Chat with local vendors and get the scoop on next week’s harvest and offerings!
We gladly accept SNAP and WIC benefits. Stop at the Information Booth for more information or to purchase your tokens.

Name: Skelly's Farm Market
Description:
Skelly\'s Farm Market is open from June-Oct with homegrown strawberries in June, sweet corn, melons, tomatoes, and other summer produce in July-Aug, Skelly\'s Sunflower Experience in late July lasting two weeks, and lots of fall fun including pumpkins, two awesome corn mazes, Choose-Your-Farm-Adventure wagons rides, and more. Plus, during all of our seasons visit our bakery with homemade donuts and more, our huge gift shop selling rustic decor, and our fantastic free playground.

Plus, visit our 8 remote roadside stands for produce in July-Aug, an see us at the Saturday Janesville Farmers Market.
